table.name: cache_handlers
table.Comment: Stores relations between cache records registered with TyghRegistry::registerCache() and tables they depend on

column.name: company_id
column.Comment: If a vendor uses custom block configuration for a container, his/her vendor ID is stored here

column.name: table_name
column.Comment: Table name the cache record depends on

column.name: cache_key
column.Comment: Cache key or prefix used to register cache record

column.name: order_amount
column.Comment: order amount - for order placement, changes and refunds

column.name: company_id
column.Comment: Company ID of the vendor who uses custom style
